#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.idxmax.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.idxmax"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:1 of
msgid "Return the row label of the maximum value."
msgstr "返回最大值的行标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:3 of
msgid ""
"If multiple values equal the maximum, the first row label with that value"
" is returned."
msgstr "如果多个值等于最大值，则返回第一个具有该值的行标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:6 of
msgid ""
"For compatibility with DataFrame.idxmax. Redundant for application on "
"Series."
msgstr "为了与 DataFrame.idxmax 兼容。对 Series 应用是冗余的。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:9 of
msgid "Exclude NA/null values. If the entire Series is NA, the result will be NA."
msgstr "排除 NA/null 值。如果整个 Series 都是 NA，则结果将是 NA。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:12
#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:14 of
msgid ""
"Additional arguments and keywords have no effect but might be accepted "
"for compatibility with NumPy."
msgstr "额外的参数和关键字没有效果，但可能会为了与 NumPy 兼容而被接受。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:17 of
msgid "Label of the maximum value."
msgstr "最大值的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:20 of
msgid "If the Series is empty."
msgstr "如果 Series 为空。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.argmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:25 of
msgid "Return indices of the maximum values along the given axis."
msgstr "返回沿给定轴的最大值的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.idxmax`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:28 of
msgid "Return index of first occurrence of maximum over requested axis."
msgstr "返回沿请求轴第一个出现的最大值的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.idxmin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:31 of
msgid "Return index *label* of the first occurrence of minimum of values."
msgstr "返回值最小值第一次出现的索引 *标签*。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:34 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:35 of
msgid ""
"This method is the Series version of ``ndarray.argmax``. This method "
"returns the label of the maximum, while ``ndarray.argmax`` returns the "
"position. To get the position, use ``series.values.argmax()``."
msgstr ""
"此方法是 ``ndarray.argmax`` 的 Series 版本。此方法返回最大值的标签，而 ``"
"ndarray.argmax`` 返回的是位置。要获取位置，请使用 ``series.values.argmax("
")``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:40 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.idxmax.idxmax_series:55 of
msgid ""
"If `skipna` is False and there is an NA value in the data, the function "
"returns ``nan``."
msgstr "如果 `skipna` 为 False 且数据中存在 NA 值，则函数返回 ``nan``。"

